{
  "text": "AGR129 human xenograft psoriasis model. Transplantation of symptomless prepsoriatic skin grafts from psoriasis patients onto immunodeficient AGR129 mice was performed as previously described [CITATION_1] , leading to the spontaneous development of a fully-fledged psoriatic phenotype within 6-8 wk.",
  "correct_citation": {
